    <body>
      <div xml:id="NA105-kiḷavi">
        <p type="edition">iḵtu iṭaiccurattu mīḷal uṟṟa neñciṉait talaivaṉ (EN, ER, ET: talaimakaṉ) kaḻaṟiyatu.</p>
        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en">This is how HE grumbles with [his] heart that experienced [the desire] to turn back in the middle of the desert.</p>
      </div>
      <div xml:id="NA105">
        <lg type="edition">
<l>            muḷikoṭi valanta muḷḷarai yilavat</l>
<l>            toḷirciṉai yatira vīci viḷipaṭa</l>
<l>            vevvaḷi vaḻaṅkum vēypayiṉ maruṅkiṟ</l>
<l>            kaṭunaṭai yāṉai kaṉṟoṭu varunta</l>
<l>            neṭunī raṟṟa niḻali lāṅka </l>
<l>            ṇaruñcurak kavalai yeṉṉāy neṭuñcēṭ</l>
<l>            paṭṭaṉai vāḻiya neñcē kuṭṭuvaṉ</l>
<l>            kuṭavaraic cuṉaiya māyitaḻk kuvaḷai</l>
<l>            vaṇṭupaṭu vāṉpōtu kamaḻu</l>
<l>            mañci lōti yarumpaṭa ruṟavē.</l>
    </lg>
       <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l rend="indent">Without talking of the 
<choice>
<seg>crossroads</seg>
<seg>distress</seg>
</choice>
 in the difficult desert,</l>
<l rend="indent">there without shade, when the water has subsided,</l>
<l rend="indent2">so that the swift-gaited elephant with [its] calf suffers,</l>
<l rend="indent2">at the rustling side of the bamboo, where hot wind wanders</l>
<l rend="indent3">noisily, dashing, so that they sway, at the resplendent branches</l>
<l rend="indent3">of the thorn-trunked silk-cotton tree wrapped by dry creepers,</l>
<l>you have experienced the long distance, heart,</l>
<l rend="indent">– so that [she] of pretty thin hair,</l>
<l rend="indent">that smells of the sky buds frequented by bees of the dark-petalled blue waterlily </l>
<l rend="indent">from the mountain pools of the western mountain of Kuṭṭuvaṉ,</l>
<l rend="indent4">undergoes difficult affliction.</l>
        </lg>
